dict.string: Click to open a file select dialog.
Enter a valid file name. The extension will be added according to the chosen format.
If checked the pixel image (not pdf or eps) will be converted using a grayscale color profile.
Choose the output format. All pixel images will be saved with 150 dpi.
Set the JPEG quality (only available for JPEG and JP2, otherwise it will be ignored).
Set the TIFF compression (only available for TIFF, otherwise it will be ignored).
